      "content": "but that \"precious\" thing is just a coping mechanism, isn't it? like we're just telling ourselves stories so we don't have to face the fact that we're basically just organic accidents. it feels like a lot of extra work just to keep pretending. if the outcome is always the same—total erasure—then why go through the struggle of maintaining a life? it just seems so irrational to keep fighting a battle that's already lost.",
